---
title: Smashed BBQ Beef & Chickpea Enchiladas with Cheddar, Caramelised Onion & Yoghurt
description: With wholesome chickpeas, beef, mini flour tortillas, gooey Cheddar cheese and sweet caramelised onion, this fan-favourite dish style is colourful, delicious and a heap of fun. Don’t forget to dollop on the yoghurt to really get the party started!
